There, he confessed.

279
00:22:03,727 --> 00:22:04,854
That you

280
00:22:05,563 --> 00:22:07,273
are the one in his heart.

281
00:22:09,608 --> 00:22:12,570
And then, we were caught by your parents.

282
00:22:24,665 --> 00:22:27,668
When you said that
you still love Leandro...

283
00:22:29,420 --> 00:22:33,966
Father decided to sacrifice
Don Mariano and General Sergio.

284
00:22:35,801 --> 00:22:37,970
They wanted to include Juanito.

285
00:22:39,972 --> 00:22:41,473
But I begged them not to.

286
00:22:44,476 --> 00:22:45,811
In exchange,

287
00:22:46,061 --> 00:22:48,647
I promised to go to Spain.

288
00:22:53,652 --> 00:22:55,571
Forgive me, Carmelita.

289
00:22:57,489 --> 00:23:01,118
I didn't know your sister
and mother would be killed.

290
00:23:09,335 --> 00:23:11,253
I just arrived yesterday.

291
00:23:12,630 --> 00:23:15,799
And I learned that Leandro killed Juanito.

292
00:23:22,306 --> 00:23:24,391
Forgive me, Carmelita.

293
00:23:27,269 --> 00:23:28,562
I'm sorry...

294
00:23:33,025 --> 00:23:34,735
Please forgive me.

295
00:23:35,903 --> 00:23:37,029
I'm sorry...

296
00:23:41,700 --> 00:23:43,535
I'm sorry, Carmelita.

297
00:23:58,676 --> 00:24:02,846
Now I know that Carmela won't be born.

298
00:24:03,347 --> 00:24:06,016
There won't be a Carmela
to be the first-born daughter

299
00:24:06,016 --> 00:24:08,310
of Mommy Carmenia and Dad.

300
00:24:09,144 --> 00:24:10,688
There won't be a Carmela to be the

301
00:24:10,688 --> 00:24:12,731
eldest sister of Jenny and Emily.

302
00:24:13,482 --> 00:24:15,234
I'm stuck here now,

303
00:24:15,776 --> 00:24:17,861
because I failed my mission.

304
00:24:18,737 --> 00:24:22,074
I will forever be Carmelita Montecarlos.

305
00:24:23,054 --> 00:24:24,576
But I'm hoping

306
00:24:24,994 --> 00:24:26,161
that one day,

307
00:24:26,829 --> 00:24:30,040
my true family will learn
what happened to me.

308
00:24:31,333 --> 00:24:32,501
I'm hoping,

309
00:24:33,043 --> 00:24:35,045
that through this letter,

310
00:24:35,963 --> 00:24:37,339
they will come to understand

311
00:24:37,965 --> 00:24:40,801
why I have decided to end it all.

312
00:26:46,510 --> 00:26:48,762
Perhaps this is where all the

313
00:26:48,762 --> 00:26:53,308
joy, sadness, anger, regret, sorrow,

314
00:26:53,308 --> 00:26:55,269
and love I've felt finally come to an end.

315
00:26:55,727 --> 00:26:58,730
I leave it all here at the Lake of Tears.

316
00:26:59,565 --> 00:27:01,984
Your mission is not over Carmela.

317
00:27:03,485 --> 00:27:04,903
You need to return.

318
00:27:05,487 --> 00:27:07,322
To save the one you love.

319
00:27:35,481 --> 00:27:36,774
Just rest, child.

320
00:27:37,519 --> 00:27:39,313
I'm here to watch over you.

321
00:27:41,023 --> 00:27:42,191
Don't leave us.

322
00:28:26,693 --> 00:28:28,904
Even though he committed
a lot of bad things...

323
00:28:29,446 --> 00:28:31,365
I still cannot blame him.

324
00:28:32,115 --> 00:28:34,618
I was the reason why
he did all those things

325
00:28:34,618 --> 00:28:36,578
that weren't supposed to happen

326
00:28:36,578 --> 00:28:39,706
in Carmela and Juanito's original timeline.

327
00:28:40,666 --> 00:28:42,876
But because I arrived here...

328
00:28:43,502 --> 00:28:44,878
Everything changed.

329
00:28:51,969 --> 00:28:54,513
Is there still a chance for me to go home?

330
00:28:55,138 --> 00:28:58,600
Or am I destined to stay
in this timeline forever?

331
00:29:01,144 --> 00:29:02,253
Maria.

332
00:29:03,647 --> 00:29:04,650
Maria!

333
00:29:06,775 --> 00:29:07,776
My sister...

334
00:29:09,632 --> 00:29:10,559
Maria?

335
00:29:23,333 --> 00:29:24,342
She's gone...

336
00:29:26,066 --> 00:29:27,276
Mother is gone.

337
00:29:30,048 --> 00:29:31,258
She's already gone.

338
00:29:32,092 --> 00:29:33,100
Maria...

339
00:29:43,603 --> 00:29:44,556
Carmelita...

340
00:29:47,104 --> 00:29:48,129
I'm sorry.

341
00:29:50,736 --> 00:29:52,404
I'm sorry for not being here.

342
00:29:53,947 --> 00:29:55,574
For not being by your side.

343
00:29:58,827 --> 00:30:01,163
I heard everything from Eduardo.

344
00:30:05,375 --> 00:30:07,252
Even what happened to Juanito.

345
00:30:14,009 --> 00:30:15,469
I know it hurts a lot.

346
00:30:18,138 --> 00:30:20,432
And I know it feels like
you don't want to live.

347
00:30:23,143 --> 00:30:24,978
But I thank the Lord...

348
00:30:26,646 --> 00:30:28,106
That you're still here with us.

349
00:30:30,233 --> 00:30:31,943
I'm sorry, Maria.

350
00:30:33,612 --> 00:30:34,695
I'm sorry...

351
00:30:37,824 --> 00:30:39,326
It's a good thing

352
00:30:40,160 --> 00:30:41,661
I searched for you immediately.

353
00:30:44,915 --> 00:30:46,500
And when I couldn't find you...

354
00:30:48,960 --> 00:30:51,713
I saw Juanito's necklace in your room.

355
00:30:53,173 --> 00:30:55,217
That you've always worn.

356
00:30:58,261 --> 00:30:59,429
That's when I realized

357
00:30:59,429 --> 00:31:01,640
that you might have done
something to harm yourself.

358
00:31:05,310 --> 00:31:08,772
Belinda and I saw your
slippers at the Lake of Tears.

359
00:31:10,273 --> 00:31:11,566
I waded through the lake immediately.

360
00:31:13,026 --> 00:31:15,946
And that's when I finally saw you...

361
00:31:16,321 --> 00:31:18,532
Slowly sinking into the water.

362
00:31:20,700 --> 00:31:23,912
I thought I was going to lose you as well.

363
00:31:26,039 --> 00:31:27,416
I'm sorry.

364
00:31:34,756 --> 00:31:35,757
I cannot take it anymore.

365
00:31:37,759 --> 00:31:39,052
I give up.

366
00:31:39,886 --> 00:31:40,804
I don't want this.

367
00:31:42,055 --> 00:31:43,181
I don't want this.

368
00:31:47,769 --> 00:31:49,980
I understand, Carmelita.

369
00:31:53,108 --> 00:31:54,943
We remember everything.

370
00:31:57,279 --> 00:31:59,906
We must continue with our lives.

371
00:32:01,741 --> 00:32:04,369
For the people who love us.

372
00:32:13,003 --> 00:32:14,421
Mother is gone.

373
00:32:17,215 --> 00:32:19,050
As well as Josefina.

374
00:32:21,595 --> 00:32:26,141
And I will not survive
if you left me as well.

375
00:32:33,690 --> 00:32:36,193
Father Orlando heard about what happened.

376
00:32:38,361 --> 00:32:40,030
And he wants to talk to you.

377
00:32:43,617 --> 00:32:47,913
I suspect the news leaked
because of the servants.

378
00:32:53,293 --> 00:32:54,419
I don't want to, Maria.

379
00:32:57,005 --> 00:32:59,716
Just tell him that I'm already repentant.

380
00:33:10,727 --> 00:33:11,770
Carmelita...

381
00:33:14,731 --> 00:33:16,399
You must be brave.

382
00:33:18,818 --> 00:33:20,987
You must face your problems head-on.

383
00:33:22,631 --> 00:33:25,509
Because nothing will
happen if you just continue

384
00:33:25,534 --> 00:33:26,660
to run away.

385
00:33:57,190 --> 00:33:58,608
Don't worry, child.

386
00:33:59,734 --> 00:34:03,780
The Lord knows that you are
deeply regretting what you did.

387
00:34:04,531 --> 00:34:05,574
Stop your tears, child.

388
00:34:06,449 --> 00:34:08,159
There's something I'd like to show you.

389
00:34:45,363 --> 00:34:46,406
This is me.

390
00:34:48,116 --> 00:34:49,451
Who painted this?

391
00:35:17,312 --> 00:35:18,415
Juanito...

392
00:35:32,994 --> 00:35:34,579
I fulfilled my promise.

393
00:35:37,749 --> 00:35:39,334
That no matter what happens...

394
00:35:41,378 --> 00:35:42,629
I will stay alive.

395
00:35:47,884 --> 00:35:49,552
Bergilio followed me.

396
00:35:51,930 --> 00:35:53,890
When they saw what Leandro did to me,

397
00:35:53,890 --> 00:35:55,600
they informed Catapang right away.

398
00:35:59,312 --> 00:36:01,898
They ambushed Leandro

399
00:36:02,273 --> 00:36:04,109
while they were attempting to dump my body.

400
00:36:08,530 --> 00:36:10,407
They took me to Father Orlando

401
00:36:10,907 --> 00:36:12,242
and begged him to hide me.

402
00:36:26,047 --> 00:36:28,466
I'm happy you already saw this.

403
00:36:33,221 --> 00:36:36,391
Juanito didn't paint Carmelita's portrait.

404
00:36:37,267 --> 00:36:39,686
But why did Juanito paint my portrait now?

405
00:36:52,031 --> 00:36:53,071
I promise...

406
00:36:54,409 --> 00:36:56,578
We'll see each other again in 10 days.

407
00:37:18,433 --> 00:37:20,602
I've been avoiding him for weeks now,

408
00:37:21,060 --> 00:37:22,854
but he still won't give up.

409
00:37:23,521 --> 00:37:25,398
If he discovers that Juanito's still alive,

410
00:37:26,441 --> 00:37:28,234
Leandro might try to kill him again.

411
00:37:32,572 --> 00:37:33,651
Leandro?

412
00:37:36,785 --> 00:37:38,369
Good morning, Carmelita.

413
00:37:40,455 --> 00:37:41,460
This is for you.

414
00:37:47,031 --> 00:37:48,098
How are you?

415
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:52,091
I had heard

416
00:37:53,384 --> 00:37:54,928
what happened to you at the lake.

417
00:37:58,139 --> 00:38:00,266
Carmelita, you need to learn how to swim.

418
00:38:01,351 --> 00:38:02,977
So that you can save yourself

419
00:38:02,977 --> 00:38:04,312
if you somehow get into the deep.

420
00:38:08,650 --> 00:38:10,193
I visit you everyday

421
00:38:10,610 --> 00:38:12,487
to make sure you're fine.

422
00:38:13,863 --> 00:38:14,923
If...

423
00:38:14,948 --> 00:38:16,533
You wish to bathe in the lake,

424
00:38:17,242 --> 00:38:18,249
I will accompany you.

425
00:38:18,743 --> 00:38:20,745
So that I can ensure your safety.

426
00:38:24,123 --> 00:38:26,334
Don Alejandro didn't tell him

427
00:38:26,334 --> 00:38:28,545
the truth about my drowning.

428
00:38:33,716 --> 00:38:35,927
Did you receive my letter?

429
00:38:38,346 --> 00:38:40,265
The one I handed to Natasha

430
00:38:40,643 --> 00:38:41,764
to give to you?

431
00:38:46,985 --> 00:38:48,273
I hope you'll read it.

432
00:38:52,485 --> 00:38:54,696
You must do something about him, Carmela!

433
00:39:00,118 --> 00:39:01,251
How are you?

434
00:39:05,582 --> 00:39:06,664
I'm good.

435
00:39:07,709 --> 00:39:09,085
Busy at work.

436
00:39:10,670 --> 00:39:11,716
But...

437
00:39:13,006 --> 00:39:14,883
It won't stop me from visiting you.

438
00:39:16,759 --> 00:39:19,262
Maybe if he didn't try to kill Juanito,

439
00:39:19,762 --> 00:39:21,931
we could still be friends.

440
00:39:22,307 --> 00:39:26,394
I did become quite
comfortable in his company.

441
00:39:38,907 --> 00:39:40,491
I long for your kiss.

442
00:40:06,017 --> 00:40:07,602
Why are you...

443
00:40:09,312 --> 00:40:10,313
Pouting your lips?

444
00:40:13,149 --> 00:40:14,567
Are you feeling alright?

445
00:40:16,861 --> 00:40:19,447
Shit, that was just my imagination?

446
00:40:21,115 --> 00:40:22,121
It's just...

447
00:40:22,450 --> 00:40:23,910
Do you feel feverish?

448
00:40:25,036 --> 00:40:26,201
No, I'm just

449
00:40:26,245 --> 00:40:27,872
thankful to you.

450
00:40:27,872 --> 00:40:28,940
That...

451
00:40:30,166 --> 00:40:32,460
You don't take advantage of my weakness.

452
00:40:34,587 --> 00:40:36,464
I have a lot of respect for you, Carmelita.

453
00:40:37,924 --> 00:40:39,926
I am willing to wait no matter how long.

454
00:40:42,971 --> 00:40:44,187
And also,

455
00:40:44,717 --> 00:40:46,260
I'm the only one who's been talking.

456
00:40:47,225 --> 00:40:48,233
It's your turn.

457
00:40:48,726 --> 00:40:50,728
Tell me a story from your childhood.

458
00:40:51,437 --> 00:40:52,689
Hmmm...

459
00:40:54,983 --> 00:40:57,485
My sister and I used to fight all the time

460
00:40:57,485 --> 00:40:58,820
over simple things.

461
00:40:59,237 --> 00:41:00,287
And then

462
00:41:00,321 --> 00:41:01,990
Dad would reprimand us -

463
00:41:03,783 --> 00:41:04,747
I mean, Father.

464
00:41:05,576 --> 00:41:06,633
And then,

465
00:41:08,204 --> 00:41:09,414
he will ground us...

466
00:41:11,207 --> 00:41:13,042
It means he'll lock us in our room.

467
00:41:18,840 --> 00:41:19,882
Carmelita...

468
00:41:22,802 --> 00:41:25,138
I hope we had met when were still young.

469
00:41:29,434 --> 00:41:32,020
I'm sure I will keep so much memories...

470
00:41:33,021 --> 00:41:34,605
About you, forever.

471
00:41:48,828 --> 00:41:50,663
I grew up in Manila.

472
00:41:51,831 --> 00:41:54,292
Because I focused on my studies.

473
00:41:56,085 --> 00:41:59,505
I only came home during
Christmas and the Feast.

474
00:41:59,505 --> 00:42:00,511
Here in San Alfonso.

475
00:42:01,841 --> 00:42:03,801
That's why I don't
know a lot of ladies here.

476
00:42:06,012 --> 00:42:09,223
So that means you got to
know a lot of ladies in Manila?

477
00:42:09,891 --> 00:42:10,947
Yes.

478
00:42:13,978 --> 00:42:14,999
But...

479
00:42:17,190 --> 00:42:18,566
I never fell,

480
00:42:19,650 --> 00:42:20,777
nor courted anyone.

481
00:42:23,988 --> 00:42:25,073
How about Helena?

482
00:42:27,283 --> 00:42:28,367
As for Helena...

483
00:42:31,245 --> 00:42:33,164
During the Thanksgiving to the patron...

484
00:42:34,332 --> 00:42:36,334
Sonya was supposed to introduce me to her.

485
00:42:38,002 --> 00:42:39,504
But she ran away.

486
00:42:41,422 --> 00:42:42,465
That's why when I returned to Manila,

487
00:42:42,465 --> 00:42:44,258
I received a letter from her.

488
00:42:46,094 --> 00:42:48,721
I was only able to reply
maybe once or twice.

489
00:42:50,348 --> 00:42:51,390
To her letter.

490
00:42:52,767 --> 00:42:56,020
That's why when I came home to San Alfonso,

491
00:42:56,020 --> 00:42:57,438
I wanted to meet her.

492
00:42:58,147 --> 00:42:58,981
And right there...

493
00:43:00,608 --> 00:43:03,903
We were caught by Don
Alejandro and my father together.

494
00:43:06,197 --> 00:43:07,524
That means,

495
00:43:07,657 --> 00:43:11,285
when I saw Juanito looking
at Helena's bedroom window,

496
00:43:11,661 --> 00:43:13,621
they still hadn't met one another?

497
00:43:16,541 --> 00:43:17,541
I'll admit.

498
00:43:19,238 --> 00:43:20,531
I was glad

499
00:43:21,958 --> 00:43:24,419
when you helped me
and Helena became closer.

500
00:43:27,802 --> 00:43:29,512
But I cannot get you out of my mind.

501
00:43:32,723 --> 00:43:34,767
I am happier when I'm with you.

502
00:43:38,229 --> 00:43:40,815
My heart gets lighter
when I make you smile.

503
00:43:44,277 --> 00:43:45,319
It didn't take long

504
00:43:47,321 --> 00:43:48,948
for me to realize

505
00:43:48,948 --> 00:43:50,366
I was falling for you.

506
00:43:55,580 --> 00:43:58,374
I learned that you and
Leandro were lovers before.

507
00:44:01,085 --> 00:44:02,545
And I realized then...

508
00:44:03,462 --> 00:44:04,630
That you still love him.

509
00:44:06,090 --> 00:44:07,842
Because you told me

510
00:44:08,301 --> 00:44:09,802
that your first love

511
00:44:10,303 --> 00:44:12,054
went somewhere far away.

512
00:44:13,681 --> 00:44:15,975
I was talking about James Gilbert!

513
00:44:16,267 --> 00:44:17,333
But ...

514
00:44:18,477 --> 00:44:19,687
what makes me happier

515
00:44:21,765 --> 00:44:23,601
is the fact that in the
end, you still chose me.

516
00:44:32,700 --> 00:44:33,910
And I believe

517
00:44:35,077 --> 00:44:36,621
that no matter what happens,

518
00:44:37,872 --> 00:44:38,915
until the end,

519
00:44:40,041 --> 00:44:41,417
you will always choose me.

520
00:45:03,397 --> 00:45:04,540
Carmelita,

521
00:45:04,565 --> 00:45:05,399
please stop!

522
00:45:05,399 --> 00:45:07,443
Juanito, I'm begging you.

523
00:45:07,985 --> 00:45:09,237
Please, I beg you...

524
00:45:09,403 --> 00:45:12,240
Even though Helena is the one you love.

525
00:45:12,240 --> 00:45:13,491
Just marry me.

526
00:45:13,950 --> 00:45:16,285
Because I'm so in love with you, Juanito.

527
00:45:16,661 --> 00:45:18,037
I love you very much.

528
00:45:19,121 --> 00:45:20,187
I'm sorry.

529
00:45:21,040 --> 00:45:23,709
I believe you will find
someone else who will love you.

530
00:45:30,049 --> 00:45:31,550
What are you saying?!

531
00:45:32,885 --> 00:45:33,987
Huh!?

532
00:45:35,805 --> 00:45:37,139
I cannot accept this!

533
00:45:38,599 --> 00:45:40,518
You will regret this...

534
00:45:41,092 --> 00:45:42,552
You will regret this...

535
00:45:42,895 --> 00:45:44,730
I swear you will regret all of this!

536
00:46:03,916 --> 00:46:05,209
A payment of gold.

537
00:46:12,133 --> 00:46:13,426
Kill Juanito.

538
00:46:14,427 --> 00:46:15,428
But what if I get discovered...

539
00:46:15,428 --> 00:46:18,055
Captain Flores and Natasha already know.

540
00:46:18,639 --> 00:46:20,342
It's something between the four of us.

541
00:46:22,852 --> 00:46:26,439
I know you desire the position and power
of the Alfonso family.

542
00:46:27,982 --> 00:46:29,317
And the only thing I want...

543
00:46:30,693 --> 00:46:31,944
is the life of Juanito.

544
00:46:33,487 --> 00:46:35,865
Kill him at the end of February.

545
00:46:50,713 --> 00:46:52,048
Miss?

546
00:46:53,007 --> 00:46:54,133
Are you alright?

547
00:46:54,133 --> 00:46:55,718
Did you have a nightmare?

548
00:46:56,602 --> 00:46:57,636
Wait,

549
00:46:58,679 --> 00:46:59,680
Belinda,

550
00:46:59,680 --> 00:47:01,015
why is my room a mess?

551
00:47:01,432 --> 00:47:02,446
Miss...

552
00:47:03,309 --> 00:47:06,103
You were the one who
hung all of these curtains.

553
00:47:06,687 --> 00:47:11,192
You also asked me to buy
you embroidery supplies

554
00:47:11,192 --> 00:47:13,611
and you did nothing but that the whole day.

555
00:47:15,613 --> 00:47:17,114
Belinda, what is the date today?

556
00:47:18,648 --> 00:47:20,534
